Package knapsack_config

Class Binary_knapsack_configuration

java.lang.Object
knapsack_config.Binary_knapsack_configuration
public class Binary_knapsack_configuration extends Object
In practice this would be a config file, not class. So it can be edited without re-compiling. Weights, values, knapsack-size for the problem domain. 1d knapsack problem. Optimal solution value: 7534 Sample data: https://developers.google.com/optimization/bin/knapsack
